## Knowledge Graph Format

Instances conforming to this ontology are stored as **RDF TriG** (`.trig`).

```
kg/
├── graph.trig              # Main Knowledge Graph (all named graphs)
└── snapshots/
    └── YYYY-MM-DD.trig     # Point-in-time snapshots
```

Instance URI pattern: `urn:openclaw:kg:{type}/{id}`
Named graph pattern: `urn:openclaw:graph:{domain}`

